========
1. Preheat the oven to 190 C / Gas 5.
2. Place prepared joint in roasting tin , and season with salt , garlic granules and pepper.
3. Add more or less seasoning to taste.
4. Roast in oven for 60 minutes ( 20 minutes per 450g ).
5. Remove from oven , cover loosely with aluminium foil , and let rest for 15 to 20 minutes.
